        <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="main-content">
      <h1>Volunteer Your Time with the Turtle Shelter Project</h1>
      <p style="text-align: center; width: 75%; margin: 0 auto;">
        Become a part of something truly transformative with the Turtle Shelter Project! We offer many opportunities to make a meaningful difference for those in need. 
        Whether you're providing financial support, helping spread awareness, or assisting in building the evests themseleves, your involvement is crucial. 
        Explore the ways you can help below and find a path that resonates with you. Together, we can create lasting change and bring hope to those who need it most!</p>

        <br>
        <div class="tabs">
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('volunteer')">Become a Volunteer</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('event')">Schedule an Event</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('home')">Volunteer From Home</button>
        </div>


      <!-- create account tab -->
      <div id="volunteer" class="tab-content">

      <!-- Text before form -->
      <p>Volunteers are at the heart of the Turtle Shelter Project, making a profound difference in the lives of the homeless by helping create quality vests for those in need. Whether you’re comfortable leading events or prefer supporting behind the scenes, your involvement is crucial.</p>
      <p>No experience, including sewing, is necessary—just a willingness to serve. You can choose the hours you’re available to help each month, as well as the days that work best for you.</p>
      <p>By volunteering, you not only help facilitate events but also ensure that each vest meets the highest standards, ensuring those who need it most receive the best. Your time and effort will have a lasting impact on the community, offering warmth, dignity, and support to those facing difficult circumstances.</p>
      <p>Become a volunteer and find opportunitis to serve near you!</p>
      <a href="/login?form=create" class="button">Sign-up Now</a>
    </div>

